'''Go To Sleep''' is a League of Legends from Thailand. They were formerly known as '''Team Toxic'''.

== History ==
'''Go To Sleep''' joined the Thailand Pro League in the 2014 season. After two years struggling in league, they finally become one of the strongest teams in Thailand and ended [[Bangkok Titans]]'s 1-year winning streak in  [[2015 Thailand Pro League/Spring|2015 TPL Spring Season]]. This result led them to qualify for the [[2015 GPL Summer]].

